The paper deals with a vision-language task that requires an AI agent to engage in a conversation with humans grounded in an image. This task involves complex multimodal reasoning, which is a common theme in computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The proposed model also involves attention mechanisms, which are commonly used in machine learning (cs.LG) and multimedia (cs.MM) research. Therefore, these five sub-categories are the most likely ones for this paper.
